X<Multiplication operator>.

Coerces both arguments to L<Numeric> and multiplies them. The result
is of the wider type. See L<Numeric> for details.

=head2 infix C«/»

=begin code :skip-test
multi sub infix:</>(Any, Any) returns Numeric:D
