X<Integer division operator>. Rounds down.

=head2 infix C«%»

=begin code :skip-test
multi sub infix:<%>($x, $y) return Numeric:D
=end code

X<Modulo operator>. Coerces to L<Numeric> first.

Generally the following identity holds:

    my ($x, $y) = 1,2;
    $x % $y == $x - floor($x / $y) * $y

