=end code

X<String three-way comparator>. Short for I<less, equal or greater?>.

Coerces both arguments to L<Str>, and then does a lexicographic comparison.

=begin code :skip-test
say 'a' leg 'b';        Less
say 'a' leg 'a';        Same
say 'b' leg 'a';        More
